{"tid":23891,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"左報狙擊港獨 批鬥浸大生搞身份認同論壇等同播獨","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T16:25:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42b85dda2aa5cfcdcadd540f852d13e9912205bb","tid":23891,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161205/280pix/1480925880_a43e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161205%2F280pix%2F1480925880_a43e.jpg&h=642f97c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》今在A2版刊登報道，以「內外勾結 獨害大學」為題，指有支持港獨成員在大學內舉行論壇，並邀請港獨人士在校園內「播獨」。文章更以特稿報道上周二由香港浸會大學傳理學會舉辦的論壇，指當日被邀出席的講者香港復興會創辦人陳云根（陳雲）和香港民族黨發言人周浩輝，與論壇主持人傳理學院一年級生廖焯嵐「裡應外合」，刻意安排二人在校園「登台播獨」。<br />\n<br />\n上周二在浸大舉行的論壇主題為《尋源歸根？割席斷交？&mdash;&mdash;談香港人未來身份認同》。報道稱，廖焯嵐疑似為「香港民族黨」成員，過往多次發表反政改言論。在考上傳理學院後刻意與學會成員混熟，以「熱心顧問」身份促成今次論壇，更稱三人瓜分為數達3,000元的「嘉賓車馬費」。<br />\n<br />\n傳理學會今發聲明指責文匯報報道失實，報道所指「車馬費」只是財政預算，並非最終支出數目。學會澄清，廖焯嵐並非如報道所指多次參與事前的籌備、構思題目及活動流程。對於論壇嘉賓全為港獨派人士，幹事會成員稱對此並非「意料之外」，全為事前擬定的目標嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56006739&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56006739%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161205&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8af445c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56006739%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161205&h=e099479a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56006739&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161205</a>"},{"pid":"80ba96b1648d0a89df978a8b08bab172c6dd0a94","tid":23891,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">更稱三人瓜分為數達3,000元的「嘉賓車馬費」</span><br />\n3000蚊都要上新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你張屌明中聯辦一幅字晝都過十萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b44b46b9b57ad4cdede69ad683d5d8b72a3682","tid":23891,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}